        "title": "JComboBox listing a String from an ArrayList of objects",
        "body": "<p>I have an <code>ArrayList<\/code> that is getting objects that contain user information from a file<\/p>\n\n<p>once the load is complete, I need the name property from each object to be loaded into a <code>JComboBox<\/code>, so that the user can choose the username to continue.<\/p>\n\n<p>this conversion from an <code>ArrayList&lt;object&gt; user --&gt; String[] strName<\/code> is where I'm having trouble<\/p>\n\n<p>any help would be greately appreciated!<\/p>\n",
